Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:06.36,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.57,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Try checking Interpol or even \Nthe Sardinian police records.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:12.50,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do these fingerprints match any records?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.40,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. There are no hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:19.78,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the boss had a previous record, \Nodds are he made sure it was erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:23.12,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But it has to be somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.92,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he tried to eliminate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.09,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,his own daughter and fears letting \Nanyone know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.65,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we look through \Nthe records of the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.30,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The boss might've faked his own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.09,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.98,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:46.12,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,A moment ago, just for a little while, \NI felt the same thing I felt in Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:48.48,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The one who got close to Abbacchio was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:50.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.90,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,This man finished Abbacchio \Nwith his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.74,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that the boss is here, Trish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:58.92,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where he is \Nright now, but he's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.45,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.45,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:06.37,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't find out the \Nboss's identity for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and kill him, we're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.88,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,We have to track down his identity first!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.73,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,No hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.05,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... The boss is meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:25.32,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to track \Nhim down any farther...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:30.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You have already tracked him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:34.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:37.92,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left now is to \Nfind a way to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:17.21,JoJo-EpTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,472)}Episodio 29 Get to the Roman Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.17,JoJo-topinternal,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting so long
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:19.38,JoJo-topinternal,Man,0000,0000,0000,,for people like you, who'd do everything \Nthey could to track this man down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.79,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(134,1)\c&H0B1DBD&\4c&H9995D1&}Screech
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.76,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Someone tracked {\i1}us{\i0} down instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno, cut the connection, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.10,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't cut me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.68,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You want to defeat Diavolo, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.10,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Diavolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:35.94,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I knew deep in my heart that someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to defeat Diavolo \Nwould eventually show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I always kept this line open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for years, filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.79,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.50,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.08,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Diavolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.91,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you said that name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:58.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't guarantee that you're on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.13,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno, cut the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.05,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,His Stand is able to skip through time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:05.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.66,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:12.23,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,you're in a hurry to find out \Nwho he is because you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.52,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,He's on our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.41,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:19.56,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,No underling of my father's could've \Nsurvived knowing his Stand ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:20.80,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Trish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.29,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't reveal more \Nabout ourselves just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.56,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.45,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,First, tell us your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,My name doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,My body is already in a state \Nthat prevents me from fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:41.67,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is whether or not \Nyou are actually able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.74,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,His ability to erase time has no weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're planning \Nto assassinate him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.06,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,but you are certain to fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:56.27,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you know of\Na way to defeat the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,His Emperor Crimson is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.23,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,But I do know of a slight \Npossibility to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.92,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a possibility, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to obtain that possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.28,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Obtain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.83,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me. Come to Rome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I can give \Nyou this possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:20.75,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think we'll go to you?\NWe don't even know if we can trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:24.63,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure at least some of \Nyou know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.00,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(172,1)\c&H418BE5&\4c&H916586&}Scr{\c&H8B7A80&}e{\c&HCF721F&}ech
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.14,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.39,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.25,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,At least, it looks just like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.12,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You must come to my \Nlocation to retrieve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:44.23,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know the true \Nway to use this arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:48.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This arrow doesn't just awaken \NStand abilities in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,There is hidden wisdom within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.56,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Come to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.92,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This arrow will defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.63,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It is your last and only hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.59,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Bring, ring, ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:13.18,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Bring, ring, ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.25,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.75,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck do you think you're \Ndoing, answering my phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.27,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,That call's for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.56,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Give it here! You stupid brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.40,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Yes, this is Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.26,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.40,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,What is, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.51,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.79,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,They've lost Abbacchio, so they should \Nbe at a loss as to what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.99,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.45,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,They've fled with no hesitation whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.59,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,They're on that boat with a goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.29,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.76,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Return to Abbacchio's last \Nlocation and look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.39,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.95,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.60,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed to look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.81,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Fear is born
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from an unexpected past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.11,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I've been fearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.66,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I found out that I had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.70,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing suspicious, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.21,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,The statue's been destroyed, but that it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.75,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I know it. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.33,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Those traitors... There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:26.05,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,They figured something out \Nthat I don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.59,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,They figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.34,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be? \NThey didn't have that kind of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.13,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that I'd never expect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.27,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:36.32,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Go after them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.28,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You have to track them down yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.60,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.35,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cioccolata and Secco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.36,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Have them stop Bucciarati and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.28,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to ask for help from such \Nfilth, but I have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.86,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:59.70,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Doppio. \NOne must destroy their fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.13,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,The moment is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.17,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,We must get through this \Nright now, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:09.24,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,That is what it means to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.44,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is this guy \Nwaiting for us in Rome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.42,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.85,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? But Bucciarati \Ndecided we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.82,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,What other options do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a little \Nstory from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:33.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,In Greenland, there's a place called \NCape York where only Inuit people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:37.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's famous for having a crater \Ncreated by a meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.09,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's said to have fallen tens \Nof thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,In 1978...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.83,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Two men from a team that was surveying \Nfor natural resources within the crater
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,contracted an unknown illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They both ended up with blisters \Nall over their bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.68,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually, they died\Nlooking like tomato sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:09.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, one of them suddenly shot \Na jolt like a stun gun from his finger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,and accidentally burned a few \Nfingers off the doctor treating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:18.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,In later investigations, \Nit was discovered that a virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,which was tens of thousands of \Nyears old, had been trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.33,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,within the meteorite inside the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:28.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That virus may have flown \Nhere on the meteorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.69,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,A virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.05,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.17,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I tracked it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.10,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This arrow is made from the same material \Nas the meteorite found in Cape York!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:46.65,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Centuries ago, a man who craved \Nabsolute power like that of the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.86,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,found out about this rock and created \Narrows from it. This is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:55.22,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This killer virus culls lifeforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is a theory called "viral evolution."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:02.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Most people who contract this virus will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,but some possess something \Nthat lets them survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.95,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,And as if it were rewarding them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,the virus gives them a new life ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:17.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This has already been proven, \Nwith your own bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.54,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what Stands are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That is the root and \Nprinciple of that arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:28.02,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.44,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But what's this secret way of using the arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.69,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that we're supposed to retrieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that until \Nyou come see me in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.62,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I can only \Ntell one of you what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:49.60,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Because no one else can ever find \Nout about this secret power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,But once you find out that method,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:57.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that it will take \Nyou to another dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:01.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It is the only way to \Ndefeat Emperor Crimson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.59,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that \Nyour story is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:13.99,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,But if the boss hears about this, \Nhe's definitely going to eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.48,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.07,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,How do you want to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.56,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the Colosseum in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.19,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get there, you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what time. \NI'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.02,JoJo-internal/narrator,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be revealed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.59,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Get up, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.66,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm gonna take a piss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.33,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.33,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.78,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the damn bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:53.65,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,There's no toilet here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.02,JoJo-main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.04,JoJo-main,Drunk,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.61,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.66,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up on land once those drunks leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.12,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll acquire a car immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.90,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,From there, we'll be in Rome \Nwithin 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.29,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,All right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.08,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.66,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's hidden behind the clouds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.47,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mista.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.89,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some drunks \Nsleeping over there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.43,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Was there some \Nkind of party tonight or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.82,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You're gonna get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.57,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.02,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:41.19,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm gonna do it, \Nso I'm gonna do it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:45.24,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! This isn't a bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.04,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.10,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:53.08,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell am I supposed \Nto reach like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:57.88,JoJo-main,Drunk 2,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to open my fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:00.50,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.36,JoJo-main,Drunk 1,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.58,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(43,1)\c&H4545BE&\4c&H6E7E7F&}Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.30,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,What'is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.14,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Stand attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:15.02,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.47,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,They were waiting for us! \NThere's an enemy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.22,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Secco.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:27.39,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you have to worry about \Nmost is running out of battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:31.18,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,Finding out later that it didn't record \Npisses me off more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.14,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.75,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
