Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Cioccolata, 34 years old. A former doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,About two years ago, he let a \Npatient die due to a simple mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he was laid off from the \Nhospital, Passione took him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.27,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He could be considered a failed elite,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:05.74,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but the boss found out his true nature \Nafter he became a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't malpractice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.74,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,He had killed patients on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.56,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He diagnosed countless people \Nwho were perfectly healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.78,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,as being sick and operated on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:25.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He'd reduce the anesthesia so the patients \Nwould wake up during surgery, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he was a young boy, \Nhe had always gotten top grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:37.73,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,When he was fourteen, he volunteered \Nto take care of the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:42.06,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, in reality, he was administering
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,unknown drugs to the \Nelderly people he looked after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.53,JoJo-flashback,cio,0000,0000,0000,,Your family hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.20,JoJo-flashback,cio,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to come visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.71,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He would say things like that every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,driving people to suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.54,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On his bookshelf at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.81,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,he had 25 video tapes of the \Nexpressions the elderly made
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,when he told them those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After driving nine elders to suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.99,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,he decided he'd become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:22.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that Cioccolata loved \Nmost was to observe people dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:27.47,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The reason he became a doctor was so \Nhe could observe people's pain and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.95,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,While watching someone die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.45,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,he felt superior to the rest of humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and felt as though he truly understood \Nthe psychology of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:42.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Cioccolata's one and only partner was Secco.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:47.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing known about him is that \Nhe's Cioccolata's former patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:52.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, they got along, \Nand Secco only follows Cioccolata's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even among the various Stand \Nusers that exist within Passione,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:00.25,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,this duo stands out as a pair of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That's who Cioccolata and Secco are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.87,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that their \Ndestination is Rome, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:16.18,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,I just received word that they \Narrived at a local fishing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.83,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:23.30,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Have Cioccolata stop and eliminate \NBucciarati and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:28.35,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,But... you must catch up to \Nthose two, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.20,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Those two... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare that I ever feel repulsed by others,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.87,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,but Cioccolata is the worst piece \Nof shit on the face of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.92,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably make a mess \Nof Rome before he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.19,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,So you think he'll go berserk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:47.23,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're going to \Ncatch up to them, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.44,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You must take control in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:55.47,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You must not let those two \Nfind out what Trish knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.28,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,nor what Bucciarati and his crew \Nare looking for in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:02.04,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.13,JoJo-main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? You're number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.42,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.51,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.68,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, was that call too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.51,JoJo-main,Dop,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.85,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hewwo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.27,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that, Mista?! \NWhen did that get on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.26,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H302112&\4c&H455F4D&}Rum{\c&H3A6966&}ble
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.87,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and find the user, Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.74,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Find out where the enemy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.45,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.97,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good! There are a ton \Nof civilians already down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.79,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's range is basically \Nthe whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.47,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,They actually involved innocent people in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:49.42,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to make \Nlooking for the user...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.09,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't tell them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.09,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Explain the situation, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.29,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,My hand just suddenly bubbled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea when this shit got on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.26,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like mold... \NIt's making my skin rip open...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.98,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's coming out \Nfrom underneath my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:09.86,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing came out of the villagers, \Nand their bodies have fallen apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.01,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good, Bucciarati!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.36,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go up on shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.90,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'll make it up \Nthe stairs to the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.07,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off getting away \Nfrom the shore on the boat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.82,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any signs of \Nbreathing on the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:22.98,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one on the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.24,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Bucciarati!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:28.46,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Until we know what attacked, \Nit's too dangerous to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:31.98,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}know{\i0} that if we go up on shore, we're gonna \Nbe attacked by whatever this thing is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.21,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.71,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(47,1)\c&H3E4A34&\4c&H303330&}F{\c&H424444&}w{\c&H382A5A&}o{\c&H320B77&}osh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.17,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.37,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.29,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where the hell is it attacking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:52.67,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.55,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.54,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mista! Don't stretch out your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:01.24,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This Stand has something like a switch \Nthat gives it the chance to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.36,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Chance to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.83,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.64,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I lowered my hand, \Nthe attack began!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.74,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nit first bubbled up on my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.76,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,after I reached into my boot to get my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.30,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,That drunk jumped down from \Nthe stairs and got attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.29,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H9191B3&\3c&H424748&\4c&HADA8B0&}Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.85,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,The other one had gone down the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.67,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,And Narancia had jumped down into the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.14,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(41,1)\c&H6F716A&\4c&H575757&\t(1043,1543, \c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}F{\c&H68686A&\t(1043,1543, \c&HFFFFFF&)}w{\c&H5F5A69&\t(1043,1543, \c&HFFFFFF&)}o{\c&H564B6D&\t(1043,1543, \c&HFFFFFF&)}osh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.81,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H743141&\4c&H610C37&}Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.58,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,So the attack begins when our \Nbodies move down to a lower location?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.31,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.27,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H67294F&\4c&H580758&}Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.15,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H553C3E&\4c&H543149&}Guuush
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.15,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you guys will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.86,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,He's not going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:42.43,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,He's not boarding the boat \Nto save the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.33,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's already figured out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.62,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,exactly how...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.78,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my Green Tea works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.68,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.34,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I've read about this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.27,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,There's a particular type of mold \Nthat inhabits the inside of a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,When that bug moves to a lower location, \Nit propagates inside it and kills it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Entomopathogenic fungus \Nand caterpillar fungus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This is very similar to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:16.73,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If you move to a lower location from where \Nyou originally were, it reacts and attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.26,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.23,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world would it work like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:23.20,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,To expand the Stand's range even further!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.10,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the mold spreads \Nfrom within the dead bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.91,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,the corpses produce more corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:32.12,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If the people move a bit further before dying, \Nthe mold's range just keeps growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.20,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:39.00,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Because the Stand ability is \Nthe user's unconscious will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.47,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Climb up, Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.13,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Get off the boat and back on shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.87,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.85,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Move forward more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.51,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,My foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:57.06,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the turtle, Narancia! \NThrow it toward Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.56,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0F1079&}P{\c&H0D1E69&}l{\c&H17424F&}o{\c&H103E4E&}p
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.16,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Narancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.08,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect. That spot's just fine!
