Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:11.49,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(71,56)\c&HA3E9FD&\4c&H017014&}B{\c&H5A8FC4&}a{\c&H304A90&}ng
