Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.75,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,You and the turtle are in \Nthe absolute perfect spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.62,sign_11970_145_Crunch,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(88,1)\c&H1419B6&\4c&H7ACEDD&}Bo{\c&H1921E3&}oo{\c&H2265DA&}m
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.63,JoJo-main,Bullets,0000,0000,0000,,Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.42,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:33.74,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we move upward, \Ntheir attack won't begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.98,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,They made it back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:41.50,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,All of those bastards made it back onto the \Nshore without a single one of them dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:48.62,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.40,JoJo-main,Cio,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Excellent.
